sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio IngressGateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Predictor as Predictor Service<br/>80/TCP or 8012/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving (RawDeployment)

    Client->>IstioGW: HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: None or Bearer Token
    IstioGW->>Predictor: HTTP (mesh internal)<br/>via VirtualService/HTTPRoute
    Note over Predictor: Init Container runs first
    Predictor->>Storage: HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials (S3/GCS/Azure)
    Storage-->>Predictor: Model Artifacts
    Predictor-->>IstioGW: Prediction Response
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService with Scheduler (llm-d)

    participant Gateway as Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant EPP as Scheduler EPP Service<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS (self-signed)
    participant Workload as Workload Pods<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS (self-signed)

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>EPP: gRPC/9002 TLS (self-signed)<br/>via Istio DestinationRule (SIMPLE)
    EPP->>Workload: HTTPS/8000 TLS (self-signed)<br/>KV-cache-aware routing
    Note over EPP,Workload: Scheduler scrapes KV-cache metrics<br/>from workload pods (8000/TCP)
    Workload-->>EPP: Inference Result
    EPP-->>Gateway: Routed Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over K8sAPI,Predictor: Flow 3: Webhook Admission

    K8sAPI->>IstioGW: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-*<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: API server cert
    Note over K8sAPI: Validates/Defaults:<br/>InferenceService, TrainedModel,<br/>InferenceGraph, ServingRuntime,<br/>Pod mutation (storage init injection)
